name: Sha Bi Guo An
body:
### Welcome to sbguoan!

Hey i am so happy that we are sharing the same opinion that GUOAN is a SHABI!

You know after these many years watching football, I never hate any team as much as I hate guoan.

There are just so tama shabi!

Oh man, I really don't know why such a stupid team can still exist in the world!!
